# Demo place — drive the arm to a fixed PLACE joint-space pose,
# hold for a short pause, open the gripper to release the
# imaginary object, then park back at init.
#
# Sibling of Demo.srv: same schema, same shape; cpp side runs
# moveArmtoDemoPlace() + place_open_pause_s sleep + controlGripper
# (demo_gripper_width) + moveArmtoInit() instead of just
# moveArmtoDemo().
#
# Together with Demo.srv (the "pick" half), DemoPlace.srv lets a
# pick_skill demo override mimic a full pick-and-place sequence
# from the pilot's perspective. For end-to-end debugging without
# pilot/atlas overhead, see /moveit_control/full_demo (raw ROS
# Trigger service exposed by the cpp executor).

# Request
bool ack
---
# Response
bool   success
string message
float32 elapsed_s
